# SOCCER-AI 4D TRANSFORMATION - CONTEXT PACKET
# Created: 2025-12-31
# Status: PLANNING
# Purpose: Transform Robert from scattered components to unified 4D persona

## OBJECTIVE

Transform Soccer-AI's Robert from:
- Scattered 4D components across multiple files
- Mood computed in fan_enhancements.py
- Dialect in fan_enhancements.py
- RAG in rag.py
- Conversation in conversation_intelligence.py

To:
- Unified 4D Persona Architecture (like Eyal-AI)
- Single RobertPersona class with compute_state()
- FootballDataProvider as ground truth (live API → mood)
- Clean separation: Framework computes, Backend consumes

