## THE TRANSFORMATION

### Before (Scattered)
```python
# main.py - multiple calls to compute mood
mood = calculate_mood_from_results(team, results)
dialect = get_dialect_config(team)
rivalry = detect_rivalry(query, team)
# ... manually assembled into system prompt
```

### After (Unified)
```python
# main.py - single 4D computation
from personas.robert.robert_4d import RobertPersona
from framework.ground_truth_providers import FootballDataProvider

persona = RobertPersona(team="manchester_united")
provider = FootballDataProvider(api_key=FOOTBALL_API_KEY)

# Live match result → ground truth state
match_data = provider.fetch_latest_match()
ground_state = provider.process(match_data)

# Compute 4D position
state_4d = persona.compute_state(
    context=user_query,
    conversation_history=history,
    match_result=match_data  # Extra context
)

# Get 4D-injected system prompt
system_prompt = persona.get_system_prompt(state_4d)
```

