## REFERENCE: EYAL-AI PATTERN

```python
# What we did in eyal-ai/pkg/conversation/chat_engine.py

class ChatEngine:
    def __init__(self):
        self.persona = EyalPersona()
        self.ground_truth = EyalGroundTruthProvider(biography_path=...)

    def chat(self, message):
        # 1. Compute 4D state
        state_4d = self.compute_4d_state(message)

        # 2. Get 4D-injected prompt
        system_prompt = self.persona.get_system_prompt(state_4d)

        # 3. Call Haiku
        response = self.client.chat(messages, system=system_prompt)
```

Apply same pattern to Soccer-AI's main.py.

